===100%===
When choosing the "Take pages" option, only 10-19 desiccated pages and tertiary drops (clue scrolls and the pet) are rolled.

With an average roll of 14.5 pages, choosing this option is worth {{Coins|{{GEP|Burnt page|14.5}}}} for [[burnt page]]s, {{Coins|{{GEP|Soaked page|14.5}}}} for [[soaked page]]s, and {{Coins|{{GEP|Soiled page|14.5}}}} for [[soiled page]]s.

